{"id":10296,"date":"2012-12-14T14:41:49","date_gmt":"2012-12-14T19:41:49","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=10296"},"modified":"2025-04-10T09:10:45","modified_gmt":"2025-04-10T05:10:45","slug":"seventy-three-sects-sahaba","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/14\/seventy-three-sects-sahaba\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Sects: Only followers of Sunnah and Sahaba enter Paradise"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>What comes over my nation will surely be what came over the children of Israel, step by step, such that if one of them fornicated with his mother, someone from my nation would do the same. Verily, the children of Israel split into seventy-two sects, and my nation will split into seventy-three sects. All of them are in the Hellfire except for one denomination.<\/strong>&#8221; They said, \u201cWho are they, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Those upon my way and the way of my companions<\/b>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2641<\/p>\n<p>Grade:\u00a0<i>Hasan\u00a0<\/i>(fair) according to Al-Arna&#8217;ut<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u064a\u064e\u0623\u0652\u062a\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0651\u062a\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u0